lead_paragraph: Though eclipsed by headline-grabbing young stars, Samantha Stosur is the only Australian to have been ranked in the top 10 in singles within the last nine years, peaking at No. 4 in 2011.

headline.print_headline: Amid Flashy Compatriots, a Player Quietly Stays the Course
headline.main: Amid Flashy Australian Compatriots, Samantha Stosur Quietly Stays the Course

snippet: Though eclipsed by headline-grabbing young stars, Samantha Stosur is the only Australian to have been ranked in the top 10 in singles within the last nine years, peaking at No. 4 in 2011.
abstract: Samantha Stosur is one of most successful Australian tennis players, yet her achievements are comparatively ignored; some blame sexism in Australia, while other says it is her humble personality.
